"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-adam-peaty-exclusive-interview-paris-olympics-swimming-b1172332.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  IfAdam Peatywas looking for a sign, there it was, screaming back at him.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sliding into the pew at the Nottingham church where he now returns every Sunday, that first time a little lost and looking for answers, the sermon that day was all about theOlympic Games.\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham\", \"score\": 0.9999999977549123, \"rank\": 1.800970585023634e-09, \"text\": \"Nottingham\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No one knew I was coming,\\\" he recalls of what has proved a seminal moment.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was just at the back and I was like, 'if this is not meant for me, then what is?'\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think society has the answers I am seeking, especially as a young man, and it's nothing to do with being an athlete.\\\"\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For almost the entirety of his career, he had the answers when it came to being the quickest breaststroke swimmer of all time: of how to win on the big days; the Olympic golds; the world titles; and yet there was still a void in his life.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has talked of the battle he has faced and come out the other side of as \\\"three years of hell\\\", a time in which he sunk into depression and became reliant on alcohol.\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Steadily, he has begun to find himself, although he readily admits: \\\"It's still very hard and it's still changing slowly.\\\"\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The origin of his turnaround began in Melbourne, where he was introduced to Pastor Ashley Null, a currently Berlin-based clergyman who works with a number of elite swimmers.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999994725314109, \"rank\": 5.270668815268019e-07, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 1412, \"end\": 1418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashley_Abbott\", \"score\": 0.9983426515790644, \"rank\": 0.0016589909119509372, \"text\": \"Ashley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashley_Abbott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashley_Abbott\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When back in Europe, the pair met up in Nottingham.\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1543, \"end\": 1553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham\", \"score\": 0.9999999977549123, \"rank\": 1.800970585023634e-09, \"text\": \"Nottingham\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty then witnessed his poignant first sermon and, as he puts it, \\\"I have been there ever since\\\".\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At theParis Olympics, his faith will be abundantly clear, as people tune in to watch his attempt to seal a hat-trick of 100metre breaststroke titles.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1804, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On his torso is a large cross with the words 'Into the Light' inked beneath it.\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are others he credits with his turnaround beyond the religious overhaul.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is his coach, Mel Marshall, who effectively threw him back in the water, warning that the clock was ticking to Paris.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2082, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6083045047952894e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then there is his girlfriend, Holly Ramsay, daughter of the celebrity chef Gordon, who has himself been a big support behind the scenes.\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2124, \"end\": 2129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9998931736747048, \"rank\": 0.00010675809199376121, \"text\": \"Holly\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Cunningham\"}, {\"begin\": 2130, \"end\": 2136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.999987113473521, \"rank\": 1.2886423000272577e-05, \"text\": \"Ramsay\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\"}, {\"begin\": 2169, \"end\": 2175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\", \"score\": 0.9984954901585736, \"rank\": 0.0015067655435233214, \"text\": \"Gordon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The biggest thing Mel did was get me back in the water six or eight weeks after I stopped, just to literally paddle,\\\" he recalls.\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She said, 'If you want to do this at the Olympics next year, you have got to just start feeling the water now'.\\\"\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was baby steps, or strokes, at first, finding his way back physically and mentally before ramping up the training at home and in Thailand before racing in Doha and finally London, where he returned to the times of old at April's Olympic trials.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2610, \"end\": 2618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5475543060476038, \"rank\": 0.8262827177391209, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2636, \"end\": 2640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0426679073517824e-18, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is something about Mel,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's extremely charismatic and extremely tough.\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Holly Ramsay posts father Gordon Ramsay's reaction to her on wedding day  Adam Peaty's family 'give up hope of reconciliation after Ramsay's wedding comment'  Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games  Discover a hidden island paradise in the Indian Ocean  \\\"You never want to lose that tough side, because you have got to make it in this sport, especially for a third Olympics.\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 3220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2892, \"end\": 2902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 2950, \"end\": 2956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.999987113473521, \"rank\": 1.2886423000272577e-05, \"text\": \"Ramsay\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have got to be asking questions, like 'how can we get faster?'\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3287, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"but ignore all the other stuff, because that's irrelevant.\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not care what other people are doing.\\\"\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3390, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That is not entirely true.\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of his major rivals for gold in Paris, Qin Haiyang, was among 23 Chinese swimmers caught up in a contamination case for the substance TMZ, for which they were cleared of any wrongdoing.\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3455, \"end\": 3460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6083045047952894e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3462, \"end\": 3473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\", \"score\": 0.9999938624998401, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Qin Haiyang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\"}, {\"begin\": 3488, \"end\": 3495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9380189138867819, \"rank\": 0.06215094655235858, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty is not here to talk of the rights and wrongs of that, but is frustrated with the World Anti-Doping Agency's handling of the case.\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3697, \"end\": 3721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Anti-Doping Agency\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As an athlete, we all want to be treated fairly and with transparency\\\"; the hope being that any doping \\\"results are not hidden and put under secrecy\\\".\", \"from\": 3747, \"to\": 3898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He, like many of his peers he says, \\\"are very disappointed in WADA\\\".\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 3967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that brings the issue of the hat-trick of Olympic titles to add to golds in his individual event in Rio de Janeiro and Tokyo.\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 4098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4073, \"end\": 4087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5456245616183518e-17, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 4092, \"end\": 4097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997781988346589, \"rank\": 0.0002218445473591121, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It gives me goosebumps any time I think of it,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 4100, \"to\": 4157, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I can not get carried away with too much thought.\", \"from\": 4158, \"to\": 4212, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not many people have done that, be dominant in the same event at three Olympics in a row.\", \"from\": 4213, \"to\": 4302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have got to make sure I keep my emotions in check.\\\"\", \"from\": 4303, \"to\": 4356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That said, he has talked in the past of \\\"swimmingangry\\\", that particular emotion getting the best out of him at key moments in his career.\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He expects that anger to bubble up come Paris, too.\", \"from\": 4497, \"to\": 4548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4537, \"end\": 4542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6083045047952894e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he does feel a different athlete and person to the one who triumphed at the Covid Games in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 4549, \"to\": 4650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4644, \"end\": 4649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997781988346589, \"rank\": 0.0002218445473591121, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There, I really relied on my ego to get the job done,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4652, \"to\": 4716, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought, 'I am the best, so I should perform the best'.\", \"from\": 4717, \"to\": 4775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now my belief system is a multitude of things.\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am almost a new person through various ways.\\\"\", \"from\": 4823, \"to\": 4870, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the metamorphosis, he hopes the result is the same.\", \"from\": 4872, \"to\": 4931, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I used to rely on my ego to get the job done... now I am almost a new person  Adam Peaty  As for what lies beyond Paris, at this stage he has no idea, so blinkered has his vision been towards his main event.\", \"from\": 4933, \"to\": 5140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5011, \"end\": 5021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 5047, \"end\": 5052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6083045047952894e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He says the next Games, in Los Angeles, by which time he will be 33, will be a target if he is still fast enough and still has the motivation.\", \"from\": 5141, \"to\": 5283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5168, \"end\": 5179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0550476549166196e-11, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And occasionally his mind wanders to the bad times possibly returning.\", \"from\": 5285, \"to\": 5355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This time around, he feels he has the support network to not spiral out of control in the same way.\", \"from\": 5356, \"to\": 5455, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have definitely got the structure, but I do not know what's ahead of me,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 5457, \"to\": 5542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some of the most evil stuff could still be ahead of me, some of the stuff that breaks people.\", \"from\": 5543, \"to\": 5637, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It would be very naive of me to say I have a structure in place and it's going to fix everything.\", \"from\": 5639, \"to\": 5737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We know the world is a very unpredictable place.\", \"from\": 5738, \"to\": 5786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All we can do is prepare and, hopefully, smile in the face of adversity.\\\"\", \"from\": 5787, \"to\": 5860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the water, Peaty was always about predictability, with the quick times and the gold medals.\", \"from\": 5862, \"to\": 5956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris, he aims to repeat that.\", \"from\": 5957, \"to\": 5990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5960, \"end\": 5965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6083045047952894e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 5992, \"to\": 6870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6052, \"end\": 6061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\", \"score\": 0.9491989094890518, \"rank\": 0.04410074051545313, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\"}, {\"begin\": 6152, \"end\": 6161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\", \"score\": 0.9491989094890518, \"rank\": 0.04410074051545313, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Benn